about.LicenseAgreement: Ngokusebenzisa le software, uyavuma ngokwemigaqo yesivumelwano selayisensi yesoftware yeNeuralium. Ungajonga uhlobo lwamva nje lwesivumelwano selayisensi yesoftware:

account.PleaseImportOrCreateWalletAccount: Nceda ungenise okanye wenze i-akhawunti ye-wallet

verifyAccount.Title: Ukuqinisekiswa kweAkhawunti
verifyAccount.IntroductionText: Ukuthintela ukuxhatshazwa, inkqubo yokudala iakhawunti kufuneka ihambe ngendlela ethile yokuqinisekisa. Kuxhomekeka kwindawo okuyo, ukhetho olukhoyo luyafumaneka.
verifyAccount.ResultsSuccess: Ukuqinisekiswa kwaba yimpumelelo! isazisi sakho se-akhawunti ngoku siqinisekiswa ngefowuni.
verifyAccount.ResultsFailure: Ukungqinisisa kwaba yimpazamo. Ungazama kwakhona kwiiyure ezingama-24.
verifyAccount.DefaultHelpText: Apha kuya kufuneka ukhethe indlela yokuqinisekisa phakathi kokhetho olukhoyo. Indlela nganye inezibonelelo kunye nezinto ezingalunganga. Nceda ukhethe eyona ilungileyo kuwe.
verifyAccount.TESTNETHelpText: Kwi-TESTNET, ukugqitha kungadluliselwa ukwenza iakhawunti kwangoko.
verifyAccount.AppointmentsHelpText: Uza kuqala inkqubo yokuqinisekisa yokuqeshwa kweNeuralium. Le nkqubo inokuhlala iintsuku ezininzi kwaye kuya kufuneka ubekhona ngexesha lokuqeshwa kwakho xa umhla uqinisekisiwe. Xabiso: engaziwa.
verifyAccount.POWHelpText: Kuya kufuneka wenze isiqinisekiso sexesha elininzi se-CPU yomsebenzi. Nje ukuba igqityiwe, iakhawunti yakho iya kuba nakho ukuba yeyam kule 1 kunye neye-2nd njengeSeva.

appointments.Title: Uqinisekiso lokuchongwa
appointments.IntroductionText: Ukuhamba komsebenzi wokuqesha kwenzelwe ukuqinisekisa abasebenzisi ekujongwe kubo ngelixa ugcina uninzi lwezikhukula ngaphandle kwenkqubo.
appointments.RequestAppointmentText: Ukuze uqale inkqubo, nceda ucele ixesha lokudibana ngokugqibeleleyo. Isicelo sokuqeshwa siya kwenziwa kwaye isiqinisekiso kufuneka sifunyenwe kwixesha elizayo.
appointments.AppointmentRequestedText: Ukuqeshwa kwakho kuphinde kwaqeshwa. Ngoku kufuneka silinde isiqinisekiso.
appointments.AppointmentConfirmedText: Isicelo sakho sokuqeshwa siqinisekisiwe kwaye umhla kunye nexesha sele libekiwe. Qiniseka ukuba ubekho ngexesha!
appointments.AppointmentVerificationRequestedText: Isicelo sokuqinisekiswa kwesikhundla sithunyelwe. Ngoku silindele isiqinisekiso.
appointments.InvalidPuzzleEngineVersion: Inguqulelo ye-injini engadingekiyo. Nceda uhlaziye inguqulelo yakho yesoftware.

puzzles.Title: Iphazili
puzzles.TimeBeforeAppointment: Iseshoni yakho yepuzzle iza kuqala kungekudala. Ixesha eliqikelelweyo elisele ngaphambi kokucela ixesha lokudibana
puzzles.WaitingForPuzzle: Iseshoni yepuzzle kufuneka iqale naliphi na ixesha ngoku. Ngoku ilindele imiyalelo ye-puzzle ...
puzzles.CompletedAndSend: Iipuzzle zakho zigqityiwe. Nceda ulinde ngelixa iziphumo zisenziwa.
puzzles.PreparingPackage: Nceda ulinde ngelixa inkqubo yokuqeshwa igcwalisa kwaye ithumele iziphumo zokungqinisisa.

sms.Title: Ukuqinisekiswa kweSMS
sms.PhoneNumberHint: Inombolo yefowuni apho unokufumana umyalezo weSMS.
sms.SmsCodeHint: Ikhowudi yokuqinisekisa ukuba uyifumene ngomyalezo weSMS.
sms.IntroductionText: Apha siza kuqinisekisa iakhawunti yakho ngokusebenzisa inombolo yefowuni eyiyo.
sms.InvalidChineseConfiguration: E-China, ngenxa yobunzima bokuthumela i-SMS, iKhowudi yokuQinisekisa eQinisekisiweyo kufuneka ifunyanwe kuqala.
sms.ResultsSuccess: Ukuqinisekiswa kwaba yimpumelelo! isazisi sakho se-akhawunti ngoku siqinisekiswa ngefowuni.
sms.ResultsFailure: Ukungqinisisa kwaba yimpazamo. Ungazama kwakhona kwiiyure ezingama-24.

accountPublication.AccountPublicationProcessExplanation: Ngaphambi kokuba kwenziwe imisebenzi kwi-blockchain, i-akhawunti yakho mayiziswe esidlangalaleni. Iakhawunti yakho iyakuqinisekiswa, kwaye iyakulungela ukusebenza xa sele iqinisekisiwe kwibhlokhi.
accountPublication.AccountPublicationFailed: Impazamo yenzekile ngelixa kushicilelwa iakhawunti. Ushicilelo aluphumelelanga.
accountPublication.CanCloseWindow: Ungavala ngokukhuselekileyo le festile ngelixa ulinde isiqinisekiso ukuba sifike.
accountPublication.NeedBlockchainSynced: I-blockchain kufuneka idityaniswe ukuze ipapashe iakhawunti.
accountPublication.NeedPeerToPublish: Akonelanga ukuba intanga iqhagamshelwe ukuze iqalise ukupapasha iakhawunti.

app.PleaseCopyYourKeyFile: Nceda ukope ifayile yakho ephambili kwi-wallet yakho.
app.TermsOfServiceCheck: Jonga apha ukubonisa ukuba ufundile kwaye uyavumelana nemimmiselo yenkonzo.
app.TermsOfServiceClick: Ngokucofa u-Ewe kunye / okanye ngokusebenzisa le software uyavuma kwimigaqo yenkonzo
app.ServerRunningStop: Iseva yeNode ye-Neuralium ngoku isaqhuba. Ngaba unqwenela ukuwuyeka?

contact.AddContactExplanation: Yongeza umfowunelwa ngokufaka i-ID kunye negama lomsebenzisi.
contact.Title: Abaqhagamshelwa
contact.Explain: Abahlobo bakho neenombolo zeakhawunti zabo zokufikelela ngokukhawuleza.

dashboard.Title: Idashboard
dashboard.Explain: Eyona ngongoma iphambili kwi-blockchain nakwiakhawunti yakho (kwii) akhawunti yakho.

history.Title: Iitransekshini
history.Explain: Imbali yakho yentengiselwano eneenkcukacha zobugcisa malunga nesakhiwo sabo sangaphakathi

mining.ExplainInfoPanel: Iinombolo ezahlukeneyo zolwazi lwe-adn malunga neeseshoni zakho zemigodi
mining.Explain: Apha ungafaka ikhompyuter yakho ukuba isebenze ngokwenza ukuba ipuzzle zemathematics ukuvula iNeuraliums entsha.
mining.Miningportalert: Qaphela: Ukuze ube ngowam, i-TCP yakho kufuneka ingene kwezinye indawo ezikwi-p2p. Ukwabelana yindlela efanelekileyo yokuziphatha kwi-p2p. Ukuba unqwenela ukumba umgodi kwindawo yesibini neyesibini zemigodi, izibuko KUFANELE lingeniswe ngenye indlela i-node ayinakuze iphumelele nakweyiphi ibhloko. Nceda uqinisekise ukuba uvula i-firewall yakho kwaye uvumele ukuhambisa phambili.
mining.ConfirmClearCachedCredentials: Ngaba kufanelekile ukucocwa kweziqinisekiso zokumbiwa kwemigodi? (oku kunokuchaphazela ukusebenza kakubi kwaye akukhuthazwanga)
mining.PortNotConnectableCantMine: Ukulungiselela ukuba kum kwimigangatho yoku-1 okanye yesi-2, i-p2p port yakho kufuneka iqhagamshelwe. Ayinakho ukwenza amandla ukumbiwa njengoko kunjalo. Ukuba awukwazi ukuvula izibuko, lungiselela ukumbiwa kwimigodi yesithathu.

neuralium.Title: Neuraliums
neuralium.Explain: Yonke into enxulumene Neuraliums kwiiakhawunti zakho

send.CantSend: Ayikwazi ukuthumela intengiselwano. Ayontanga yontanga ingene.
send.NoAccountOrAccountNotActiveOrNotPublishe: Akukho akhawunti, iakhawunti ayisebenzi okanye ayishicilelwanga
send.PleaseChooseContactInTheListOrInputConta: Nceda ukhethe umfowunelwa kuluhlu okanye kwi-id yokunxibelelana
send.Title: Thumela
send.TransactionError: Kwenzeke impazamo ekuthumeleni intengiselwano. Iikhowudi zempazamo:
send.NotesDescription: Inqaku lokuzikhethela eligcinwe kwiirekhodi zakho kuphela.

server.CheckingServer: Nceda ulinde ngelixa siqinisekisa ukuba iseva esebenzayo ikhona ...
server.Title: Umncedisi
server.Explain: Iwindows yabasebenzisi abaphambili abavumela ukuba balawule umncedisi weNodi ye-Neuralium.

settings.Title: Useto
settings.Explain: Iindlela ezahlukeneyo onokuzihlelela ukwenza imali kwi-wallet yakho.

tools.Title: Izixhobo
tools.Explain: Izixhobo eziluncedo ukunceda ukuphucula amava akho e-Neuralium.

testMode.ParagrahOne: Okwangoku ukwimo yeTESTNET. Inguqulelo ye-testnet yenzelwe ukubavavanywa ngezinto ezintsha ezinokuthi okanye zinokungasebenzi ngendlela ebezicwangcisiwe. Unokuxela nayiphi na ibugs, iingxaki okanye iingcebiso onokuba nazo kwizisombululo zethu ezinikezelweyo.
testMode.ParagrahTwo: Kwindlela ye-TESTNET, naziphi na iithokheni ze-neuralium ezifunyenweyo zenzelwa iinjongo zovavanyo kuphela kwaye azinakusetyenziswa kunxibelelwano 'MainNet' womnatha. Iipokhethi ezifunyenwe kwimodi ye-TESTNET nazo zingalahleka okanye zenziwe nangaliphi na ixesha ngaphandle kwesaziso sangaphambili.
testMode.Warning: I-node kunye ne-wallet okwangoku zikwi-TestNet Mode kwinethiwekhi eyahlukileyo.
testMode.Period: Olu lwakhiwo lweTESTNET lusebenza kude kube nge-18 ka-2020.

wallet.PleaseCreateOrCopy: Yenza i-wallet entsha okanye ulayishe esele ikho.
wallet.WalletWaitMessage: Ngoku sakha iakhawunti kunye nezitshixo zokhuseleko. Oku kunokuthatha imizuzu emininzi. Enkosi ngonyamezelo lwakho.
wallet.Completed: Isipaji sakho senziwe ngokufanelekileyo. Ngoku njengenyathelo elilandelayo, sicebisa ukuba wenze ugcino lwokhuseleko kwifowulda yakho yonke. Sikwakhuthaza kakhulu ukuba ususe ngokomzimba isitshixo esiphezulu kwifolda yakho yeakhawunti kwaye usigcine ngokukhuselekileyo kwikhomputha ngaphandle kwekhompyuter yakho.
wallet.WalletPath: Unokufumana isikhwama sakho esitsha kule ndlela ilandelayo
